🎟️ FlashTix Live
⚡ Real-Time Ticketing Platform 
<p align="center"> <em>High-performance distributed system built for extreme flash-sale traffic</em> </p>
🚀 Overview

FlashTix is a scalable, event-driven ticketing platform designed to handle massive concurrent users during flash sales.

It ensures:

⚡ Instant response (no API blocking)
🔒 Zero data loss
🌐 Real-time updates across all users
🛡️ System stability under heavy load
✨ Core Features
🚪 API Gateway with Rate Limiting (prevents overload)
🧠 Event-Driven Architecture using Kafka
⚡ Real-Time Updates via WebSockets
🔄 Asynchronous Order Processing
🛡️ Fault Tolerance with Circuit Breaker
📄 Background PDF Ticket Generation
📦 Object Storage (MinIO)
🏗️ System Architecture
<p align="center"> <img src="./assets/System-Architecture.png" width="900"/> <br/> <em>End-to-end flow: Gateway → Kafka → Processing → Redis → WebSocket → RabbitMQ → MinIO</em> </p>
🧰 Tech Stack
⚙️ Backend
Java 17+ / Spring Boot
Spring Security + JWT
Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
🚪 API Gateway
Spring Cloud Gateway
Redis (Rate Limiting - IP based)
🧱 Infrastructure
MySQL (Primary DB)
Redis (Caching + Rate Limiting)
Apache Kafka (Event Streaming)
RabbitMQ (Background Jobs)
MinIO (Object Storage)
🎨 Frontend
React + Vite
Axios (JWT interceptors)
STOMP + SockJS (WebSockets)
🔄 Request Flow
Client sends request → API Gateway
Gateway applies rate limiting (Redis)
Request forwarded to backend service
Order pushed to Kafka
Consumer processes order + updates DB
Redis cache updated
WebSocket broadcasts real-time updates
RabbitMQ triggers PDF generation
Ticket stored in MinIO
⚙️ Local Setup
1️⃣ Start Redis
docker run -d --name redis-stack -p 6379:6379 redis/redis-stack-server:latest
2️⃣ Setup MySQL
CREATE DATABASE flashtix;
3️⃣ Start API Gateway
cd flashtix-gateway
./mvnw spring-boot:run
4️⃣ Start Backend
cd flashtix-backend
./mvnw spring-boot:run
5️⃣ Start Frontend
cd flashtix-frontend
npm install
npm run dev
📡 API Endpoints
🔐 Authentication
POST /api/auth/register
POST /api/auth/login
POST /api/auth/refresh
🎤 Events
GET  /api/events
POST /api/events (Admin)
🎟️ Orders
POST /api/orders/purchase
GET  /api/orders/my-tickets
GET  /api/orders/{id}/download
